Sekemwize kuvwiziligwa. "Mbwiya zihile zowifya tabia inogile."
Mweye muiteganye, muleke uhasanyi wenu! Wamwenga wenu hawamanyile bule Mulungu. Nowalongela vino muladi muwe na chinyala.
